            "heading_id": "today",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "richtext_zP9KFN": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>There are a plethora of factors that influence the Gold prices on a daily, and sometimes hourly basis. Knowing the current Gold Rate is important if you’re planning on making a purchase or a valuable investment. Here are some Gold Rates you should keep an eye out for when purchasing or gifting Gold today:</p><ul><li>Traditionally speaking, 10 gram Gold price today is the most popular benchmark quote searched. </li><li>For smaller purchases and investments, you should check the per gram Gold Rate today. </li><li>Making a small, casual purchase? Check out the updated 2 gram Gold price for an informed decision. </li><li>Shopping for your Wedding or <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Engagement</span></a>? Then checking the 7 gram gold price today for necklaces, and 2 gram gold prices for <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">earrings</span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rings</span></a> is imperative. </li><li>If you’re planning a big investment, keep a close watch on the 1 tola gold price and 1kg gold price to enter the market at the right time. </li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "heading_zcpg3M": {
          "type": "heading",
          "name": "Geographic Variations And City-Wise Gold Rates",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Geographic Variations And City-Wise Gold Rates",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_id": "geographic",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "richtext_86xxpT": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>At a given point, every city, due to various factors, has varying levels of demands which impacts the price of gold in that city. For example, Gold Rate in Mumbai or Gold Bombay Rate, usually differs to the Gold Rate in Delhi, Gold Rate in Chennai or Gold Rate in Kolkata at any given time. For best results, it is ideal to look for the Gold Rates of whichever city you’re living in. For example, if you’re from Mumbai, you should look at the Gold Rate Today in Mumbai live before making a jewelry purchase of a big investment as the live rates will give you the most accurate pricings on the basis of recent trades.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_GA4FHb": {
          "type": "heading",
          "name": "Hallmarked Gold Rates",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Hallmarked Gold Rates",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_id": "hallmarked",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "richtext_8iFNUR": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>As hallmarking has become a legal compulsion in most states, most platforms online have reflected the same. It is understood that when you check the gold rate today, what you see is the hallmark gold rate today as BIS hallmarking is necessary to ensure quality, purity, and authenticity. </p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_wgpbqB": {
          "type": "heading",
          "name": "Investment Tips!",
