        },
        "richtext_RrHAQY": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Stay updated with the latest gold coin price and gold coin rates at your nearest outlets as festivities approach. Gold coins are an excellent modern choice for auspicious gifting during these occasions. </li><li>Need to plan a gift for someone who lives far away? You can buy a gold coin for them online and get it delivered to their doorstep. This is a popular choice for children studying or working in foreign countries. </li><li>For smart investors looking to make a big purchase, keep an eye on the gold biscuit price and gold bullion price today for strategic investments. </li><li>If you’re looking at Gold from a purely investment standpoint, you can consider buying gold from a bank to ensure purity and documentation. </li></ul>"
